WEBVTT

00:01:58.764 --> 00:02:00.562
7:00: Treasure

00:02:00.798 --> 00:02:01.798
(Roar)

00:02:02.196 --> 00:02:05.841
As a result, the hero
claims some treasure,

00:02:05.865 --> 00:02:07.300
special recognition, or power.

00:02:08.251 --> 00:02:09.953
8:00: Result

00:02:09.977 --> 00:02:12.197
This can vary between stories.

00:02:12.221 --> 00:02:14.392
Do the monsters bow down before the hero,

00:02:14.416 --> 00:02:18.323
or do they chase him as he flees
from the special world?

00:02:18.347 --> 00:02:19.850
9:00: Return

00:02:20.663 --> 00:02:23.748
After all that adventure,
the hero returns to his ordinary world.

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:27.145
10:00: New Life

00:02:27.169 --> 00:02:31.082
This quest has changed the hero;
he has outgrown his old life.